item.dc:creator: @uberpk3r uberpk3r
item.description:
@uberpk3r wrote:

[quote=“SVU, post:18, topic:377232”][quote author=uberpk3r link=topic=473137.msg3461171#msg3461171 date=1294494528]

Honestly That the source is leaked doesn’t matter at all, -I mean everyone that host it will fail as everyone else failed.
Aftermath will stay up and people will play it. whats changed is that its become a open source.
Again who the fuck cares ?

I said it before and I say it again pomp is a complete retard and only reason why hes in the team is because hes wallet lawl

A retard calling others a retard?

Who the fucks cares about what you think, Theres not a single person who gives u the slightest bit of respect other than crooks.

Pom’s doing a great job, If its for his wallet or not, Your just jealous because your wallet wasnt big enough to fund your server and fund meatdicks payments for half assed coded shite.

I could say the same about you.
Doesn’t matter who cares about my opinion Its a free forum I speak my mind w/e I want kid.
You on the other hand are complete unknown here there for you have most certainly not a opinion here.
Pom is the reason why the whoel team got hacked so yea you right hes doing a great job, do you hear your self?

I quess this is from a retard to a retard then?
[/quote]
Our DB getting leaked literally didn’t do a single thing to our server, at all. Sure it might effect Emulation or other servers because people constantly use the same passwords for unknown reasons… We have a great team, and we got over the leak\hack\fuck over(whatever you wanna call it) pretty fast.[/quote]

Yea, I mean it isn’t the world end ,keep the server online and people wont give a fuck about the source is released or not , but its still pomp big ass fault and I know for sure pomp cannot code java nor php. whats left other then a friendly face and the money?

Honestly I don’t care, just added my opinion on the whole thing.
